{"tid":2192042,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌，訓醒仲係好嬲，想一鎚打爆個電話，有冇人都有同感？","createTime":"2020-09-07T00:57:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T23:52:33.000Z","uid":57328,"like":33,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"b212847c3396ae0098666b141681bc00dfae3e9d","tid":2192042,"uid":57328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T00:57:15.000Z","msg":"Twitter極度缺人 可以講得上踏入嚴寒<br />\n大家唔係話好撚中意香港咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明Twitter 好有用而且開始有成效<br />\n大家係懶定係驚？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見到人數漸少 我真係心都寒埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"orange\">應承我唔好放棄，大家一齊努力好無？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span><br />\nTask1 collection <br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/tweet4hk/timelines/1284502565149802498\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftweet4hk%2Ftimelines%2F1284502565149802498&d=YmBpLFXYotmGfWLbQLkNp8eYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=a52460b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/tweet4hk/timelines/1284502565149802498</a><br />\nTask2 collection <br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/tweet4hk/timelines/1284502572531716096\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftweet4hk%2Ftimelines%2F1284502572531716096&d=YmBpLFXYotmGfWLbQLkNp8eYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=bb63f731\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/tweet4hk/timelines/1284502572531716096</a><br />\nTask4 collection <br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/tweet4hk/timelines/1284502605960409089\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftweet4hk%2Ftimelines%2F1284502605960409089&d=YmBpLFXYotmGfWLbQLkNp8eYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=46f081e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/tweet4hk/timelines/1284502605960409089</a><br />\n<strong><span class=\"violet\">collection 會逾時，同埋唔會更新，如果睇唔到就入Twitter bot睇啦。<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nTwitter 手足整咗個網站出嚟比大家做task<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以後大家無藉口喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n快啲bookmark 佢啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://act4hk.com/twitter\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fact4hk.com%2Ftwitter&d=YmBpLFXYotmGfWLbQLkNp8eYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=6c897dfe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://act4hk.com/twitter</a><br />\n<br />\n入bot 拎24小時更新：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=YmBpLFXYotmGfWLbQLkNp8eYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=ef011b29\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n<br />\nTwitter有APP喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\niOS: <a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/tweet-hk/id1488588896?l=en\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fhk%2Fapp%2Ftweet-hk%2Fid1488588896%3Fl%3Den&d=YmBpLFXYotmGfWLbQLkNp8eYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=4fc3312a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/tweet-hk/id1488588896?l=en</a><br />\nAndroid: <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.tweethk.app\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.tweethk.app&d=YmBpLFXYotmGfWLbQLkNp8eYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=2e1ea4eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.tweethk.app</a><br />\n<br />\n或者download 香城online 個app 都有Twitter做<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/HKOnlinePortal\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FHKOnlinePortal&d=YmBpLFXYotmGfWLbQLkNp8eYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=82ba792b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/HKOnlinePortal</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong><span class=\"x-large\">Like retweet reply</span></strong></span><br />\n*如果見到想用嘅圖已經有手足用咗請搵第二張圖<br />\n*如果見到已經有好多圖就唔好再放圖，只留文字（短短地都得）<br />\n*唔好只係扔低張圖咩字都唔打<br />\n*唔知留咩好就like 手足留言或者啲對我哋有利嘅留言<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><strong><span class=\"gold\"><br />\n將Twitter 變成日常，每人每日做少少。<br />\n每人嘅一小步加埋就係一大步。<br />\n我哋唔知做咩先有用，所以咩都試下咩都做下。</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"313d4391f931a89b0ecf75d606d8c47ee28e4b0e","tid":2192042,"uid":63774,"like":4,"dislike":8,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T00:58:16.000Z","msg":"嬲完記得返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79b06a8e47767bc52582357543f96f8223273563","tid":2192042,"uid":8014,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T01:00:02.000Z","msg":"好嬲但都係番左工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要賺錢先可以撐住黃圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bee30b9bc4dd0c08bacb6386a8597eac1ad6041e","tid":2192042,"uid":57328,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"79b06a8e47767bc52582357543f96f8223273563","tid":2192042,"uid":8014,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T01:00:02.000Z","msg":"好嬲但都係番左工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要賺錢先可以撐住黃圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T01:01:03.000Z","msg":"波蘭打要戒嚴三年，最低收費抗爭十年先有自由，大家加油"},{"pid":"499d33f3e88204c7205035cd66dcdaaaed8b3ef5","tid":2192042,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T01:01:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"edfbbe30d5d64f3fa8b305112cc99813580cc8ed","tid":2192042,"uid":85030,"like":1,"dislike":0